Gottschalk joined Volbeat in 2002 replacing their original guitarist Teddy Vang.
In the late 1990s, he joined Dominus and played bass on their final record "Godfallos" in 2000.
A year later, Dominus split-up and their singer Michael Poulsen founded Volbeat.
